This is a template automation project with Python and Selenium.

There are 2 options to run the project.
1. MacBook M1
_ Install python3.
_ Install ChromeDriver and Chrome.
_ Go to project and run: pip3 install -r requirements.txt
_ Run tests: pytest exercise1.py
 
2. Non MacBook M1
_ Install Docker.
_ Run: docker build -t python-poc .
_ Run: docker run -it -w /app -v $(pwd):/app python-poc:latest bash
_ Run: pytest exercise1.py

Now you can continue working on the project.

